Summary: UFO over Michigan ave and the Chicago River?
divs: Sighting DetailsOn 10-27-2011 I snapped a photo of the Michigan Ave bridge in Chicago looking North. At the time I didn't notice anything but when I got home and uploaded the photos later that night I noticed something in the sky on the photo. Not sure if it was some weird reflection from the city lights or what but I am uploading the photo with this so I will let you be the judge.
